Package: RcppDeepState
Type: Package
Title: A simple way to fuzz test code in Rcpp packages
Version: 2.0
Author: Akhila Chowdary
Maintainer: Fabrizio Sandri  <sandri.fabr@gmail.com>
Description: An implementation of an advanced fuzz testing tool to find subtle bugs
  in Rcpp packages. RcppDeepState combines the advantages of both DeepState and
  Valgrind to obtain a sophisticated tool that checks for errors inside the Rcpp 
  code.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: RcppArmadillo,RInside,data.table,Rcpp,methods,qs,nc,xml2
Suggests: testthat,
    here,
    devtools,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
VignetteBuilder: knitr
